7 An Act relating to county jails; directing the county
sheriff to create an Orange Alert communication
8 system; requiring posting of information about the
communication system in local newspaper; requiring
9 residents to register for notifications; directing
the county sheriff to promulgate policies and
10 procedures; providing for codification; and providing
an effective date.
